'''大窗钩蛾属'''（[[学名|屬名]]：{{snamei|Macrauzata}}{{NoteTag|1=由[[豆斑钩蛾属|豆斑钩蛾属]]的屬名 ''Auzata'' 加上前綴詞 ''[[wiktionary:macr-|macr-]]''（長的）而來，係指其翅脈的生長模式<ref>{{cite book | last = Butler | first = A. G. | title = ''Illustrations of typical specimens of Lepidoptera Heterocera in the collection of the British Museum'' | volume = 7 | year = 1889 | url = https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/75387#page/53/mode/1up | access-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211112134658/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/75387#page/53/mode/1up }}</ref>。}}}}）是[[鱗翅目|鱗翅目]][[钩蛾科|钩蛾科]]的一個[[属_(生物)|属]]，主要分布於[[東洋界|東洋界]]，在其外的[[日本|日本]]、[[中國|中國]]中北部<ref name = foc>{{ cite book | author = 朱弘复、王林瑶 | chapter = 大窗钩蛾属 | title = 中国动物志：昆虫纲 第三卷：鳞翅目 圆钩蛾科 钩蛾科 | publisher = 科学出版社 | year = 1991 | page = 173 | isbn = 7-03-001906-7 }}</ref>與[[蘇拉威西|蘇拉威西]]亦有物種分布<ref>{{cite book | last = Holloway | first = J. D. | chapter = "''Macrauzata'' Butler" | title = ''The Moths of Borneo 8: Castniidae, Callidulidae, Drepanidae, Uraniidae'' | publisher = Southdene | year = 1998 | chapter-url = https://www.mothsofborneo.com/part-8/drepaninae/drepaninae_5.php | access-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-date = 2020-01-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200114062654/http://www.mothsofborneo.com/part-8/drepaninae/drepaninae_5.php }}</ref><ref>{{ cite book | author = 中島秀雄 | chapter = カギバガ亜科 | editor = 岸田泰則 | title = 日本産蛾類標準図鑑 | volume = 1 | publisher = -{学研プラス}- | year = 2011 | isbn = 978-4-05-403845-5 | pages = 112-126 }}</ref>{{rp|118}}。[[喙|喙]]发达，[[触角|触角]]双栉形，翅缰发达，其显著特征为前后翅中部各有一个透明的大窗，故名<ref name = foc/>。

